Text.string: Ugh. The Children of the Vault have been leavin' these suck-butt Calypso idols all over the place. You know what? We're gonna stick it to those wannabe gods and make our own idols, in MY image! From chiseled jaw to legendary calves! First off, go find all my wanted posters.

I didn't go from Hyperion accountant to bandit warchief just to follow orders again. But, y'know, after I refused to join that stupid cult, Tyreen Calypso put a bounty on my sculpted ass. And the rest of me, too! But I'm still alive, baby! And still shakin' it, bro!
Who do those Calypso Twins think they are, anyway? Gods? Y'know, someone called my pecs divine once. That's... pretty much the same thing.
Whoa, that magic box can print anything! That sure is convenient and helpful, don't ya think?
Vaughn, know anything about these COV statues?
Hey, Vaughn. Know anything about these little COV statues?
Vaughn. I have discovered a COV statue. Know anything about it?
Vaughn, boyo, know anything about these little COV statues?
All right. Now feed those wanted posters into the scanner! Wow, I'm really walkin' you through this, aren't I?
Well?! How'd they turn out?

Ugh. The Children of the Vault have been leavin' these suck-butt COV statues all OVER the place. You know what? We're gonna stick it to those wannabe gods and make our own idols. In MY image! Yeah, good idea! From chiseled jaw to legendary calves! First off, go find all my wanted posters. P.S., I am very wanted.
Nice bod, bro.
Looking fit. Almost as built as me, heh. Almost.
You are a prime physical specimen.
What a looker.
Oh, come on, I know... Now let's swap out some of those crappy old Calypso statues for some of my perfection!
Oh, come onnnn, I know... Now, let's swap out some of those crappy old COV statues for some of my “perfection”, as you so rightly put it.
Vaughn, know anything about these Calypso statues?
Hey, Vaughn. Know anything about these little Calypso statues?
Vaughn. I have discovered a statue of the Calypsos. Know anything about it?
Vaughn, boyo, know anything about these little Calypso statues?

If we're gonna pull this off, we're gonna need those pictures of me to feed into the 3D scanner thing. Then we can start printin' out the statues that look like me instead! Ha ha! That'll really tick off the Calypsos.
Okay, now hit the button and print those bad boys! I mean, if it can handle my angles. You know what I'm talking about.
So long, Calypsos!
And hello glorious golden Vaughn! Ohhh, man, look at me now. Got my own statue, just joined up with the number one clan on the planet... Go Crimson Raiders! I love this day!
Take that, Calypso jerks!
Annd, that's me! Y'know what makes the Crimson Raiders so great? Y'all kick ass like CRAZY AND protect the weak. Now that is the kind of clan I can get behind!
Love that smashing sound!

When the Calypsos see my golden visage, they're gonna be PISSED! Y'know, some day, maybe I'll give the whole “bandit warchief” thing another go, but for now, I'm really good rollin' with you and smashing the COV into dust! Anyway, thanks for your help! And, uh, come see me when you have a chance!

I remember that picture being taken! Ha! Man, we've come a long way since bandit selfies. Y'know, back when I started my FIRST bandit clan, if you wanted an image of yourself, you gotta bloody up your face real good and then smash it on a rock!

Thanks, Vault Hunter! You made my dreams come true! I mean, who DOESN'T want little golden statues of themselves? Am I right? Y'know, we may not have destroyed the COV today, but once they see those statues, they're gonna know who's in charge! They'll know!
You hear that, Tyreen?! Now worship at the altar of my abs! For my name is Vaughn!
So long, COV!
Ohhh, the magic box gave us a new offering!

Now THAT is a quality wanted poster. It really shows off the ol' blood hand. Started wearing that during blood feud number two. No, it was three! That's right, 'cause number two was the time I declared war against a mountain. Guess which one's still standin', bro! Death to mountains!

Don't remember anyone snagging that picture, but I can't blame 'em! Those are my trusty Hyperion Redbar X-2000's with quicksilver fly, and no-rise banding. Oh, best underwear in the universe, bro! It's the only good thing Hyperion ever gave me.
I killed a guy for a pair of those once! Nice fella.
I understood, like, three of those words.
No-rise banding. Nice.
They sound... delightful.
Just between you and me...||... they're the source of all my power. Shhhhh.

Okay, we've got some great images of my righteous bandit bod. Now, the COV have a 3D printer nearby that's producing those statues. Scan the wanted posters into the printer so we can print statues of me instead!
